Resource Profile: openIMIS CommunicationRequest

Official URL: https://github.com/openimis/openimis_fhir_r5_ig/StructureDefinition/openimis-communication-request Version: 0.1.0
Draft as of 2025-08-26 Computable Name: OpenIMISCommunicationRequest

Defines a CommunicationRequest for openIMIS which maps to the Claim request for feedback in openIMIS.

Usages:

  • Refer to this Profile: openIMIS Claim Response
  • Examples for this Profile: CommunicationRequest/Claim001CommunicationRequest
  • CapabilityStatements using this Profile: openIMIS Capability Statement

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
